{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. H\u00e9 1:1-3; 4:1; 12:25.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi nous devons d\u2019autant plus nous attacher aux choses que nous avons entendues, de peur que nous ne soyons emport\u00e9s loin d\u2019elles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.1.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Car, si la parole annonc\u00e9e par des anges a eu son effet, et si toute transgression et toute d\u00e9sob\u00e9issance a re\u00e7u une juste r\u00e9tribution,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>comment \u00e9chapperons-nous en n\u00e9gligeant un si grand salut, qui, annonc\u00e9 d\u2019abord par le Seigneur, nous a \u00e9t\u00e9 confirm\u00e9 par ceux qui l\u2019ont entendu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Dieu appuyant leur t\u00e9moignage par des signes, des prodiges, et divers miracles, et par les dons du Saint-Esprit distribu\u00e9s selon sa volont\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-18: cf. (Ps 8:5-7. Ph 2:6-11.) (Ga 4:4, 5. Jn 20:17.) H\u00e9 5:7-10; 4:15, 16.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>En effet, ce n\u2019est pas \u00e0 des anges que Dieu a soumis le monde \u00e0 venir dont nous parlons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Or quelqu\u2019un a rendu quelque part ce t\u00e9moignage:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Qu\u2019est-ce que l\u2019homme, pour que tu te souviennes de lui,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">ou le fils de l\u2019homme, pour que tu prennes soin de lui?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Tu l\u2019as abaiss\u00e9 pour un peu de temps au-dessous des anges,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">tu l\u2019as couronn\u00e9 de gloire et d\u2019honneur,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\n    Tu as mis toutes choses sous ses pieds.<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">En effet, en lui soumettant toutes choses, Dieu n\u2019a rien laiss\u00e9 qui ne lui f\u00fbt soumis. Cependant, nous ne voyons pas encore maintenant que toutes choses lui soient soumises.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mais celui qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 abaiss\u00e9 pour un peu de temps au-dessous des anges, J\u00e9sus, nous le voyons couronn\u00e9 de gloire et d\u2019honneur \u00e0 cause de la mort qu\u2019il a soufferte, afin que, par la gr\u00e2ce de Dieu, il souffr\u00eet la mort pour tous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il convenait, en effet, que celui pour qui et par qui sont toutes choses, et qui voulait conduire \u00e0 la gloire beaucoup de fils, \u00e9lev\u00e2t \u00e0 la perfection par les souffrances le Prince de leur salut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Car celui qui sanctifie et ceux qui sont sanctifi\u00e9s sont tous issus d\u2019un seul. C\u2019est pourquoi il n\u2019a pas honte de les appeler fr\u00e8res,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>lorsqu\u2019il dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    J\u2019annoncerai ton nom \u00e0 mes fr\u00e8res,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je te c\u00e9l\u00e9brerai au milieu de l\u2019assembl\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et encore:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Je me confierai en toi.<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">Et encore:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Me voici, moi et les enfants que Dieu m\u2019a donn\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ainsi donc, puisque les enfants participent au sang et \u00e0 la chair, il y a \u00e9galement particip\u00e9 lui-m\u00eame, afin que, par la mort, il an\u00e9ant\u00eet celui qui a la puissance de la mort, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire le diable,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.15","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:15","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>et qu\u2019il d\u00e9livr\u00e2t tous ceux qui, par crainte de la mort, \u00e9taient toute leur vie retenus dans la servitude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.16","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:16","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Car assur\u00e9ment ce n\u2019est pas \u00e0 des anges qu\u2019il vient en aide, mais c\u2019est \u00e0 la post\u00e9rit\u00e9 d\u2019Abraham.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.17","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:17","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>En cons\u00e9quence, il a d\u00fb \u00eatre rendu semblable en toutes choses \u00e0 ses fr\u00e8res, afin qu\u2019il f\u00fbt un souverain sacrificateur mis\u00e9ricordieux et fid\u00e8le dans le service de Dieu, pour faire l\u2019expiation des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s du peuple;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.18","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 2:18","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>car, ayant \u00e9t\u00e9 tent\u00e9 lui-m\u00eame dans ce qu\u2019il a souffert, il peut secourir ceux qui sont tent\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbd11dba8.96319852');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd11dba8.96319852\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbd11dba8.96319852","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbd11dba8.96319852'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd11dba8.96319852\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}